#

Classic Beef Bolognese

$25
550 kcal

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodPasta Sauce

Description

A rich and hearty Italian meat sauce, perfect for pasta or as a topping for polenta, simmered to perfection with herbs and vegetables.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef: 6 lb
  • Olive Oil: 1/4 cup
  • Onion, diced: 1 large
  • Carrot, diced: 1 large
  • Celery, diced: 1 stalk
  • Garlic, minced: 4 cloves
  • Crushed Tomatoes: 2 cans (28 oz each)
  • Tomato Paste: 2 tbsp
  • Red Wine: 1 cup
  • Bay Leaves: 2
  • Dried Oregano: 2 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Fresh Basil, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • Parmesan Cheese, grated (optional): for serving
